# Requirements for CS 601 term project

- Must be a mobile-first design.
- These are the CSS requirements that must be met in aggregate across the whole project. When implementing something that matches this requirement, flag it in a comment.
    - Must use at least 10 descendent selectors
    - Must use at least 10 unique adjacent selectors
    - Must have 20+ different class selectors
    - Must have at least 20 #id selectors
    - Must have 15+ pseudo-element selectors
    - Must have 15+ pseudo-class selectors
- Must use axios, fetch, or some other modern equivalent. The minimum number of ajax features is 12 ajax invocations actively used. You cannot use XHR.